headline: CrowdStrike Taps Aramco And NordVPN To Expand Security Growth Story
summary: CrowdStrike Holdings (NasdaqGS:CRWD) signed a memorandum of understanding with Saudi Aramco to support national level cybersecurity and AI transformation in Saudi Arabia. The Aramco agreement includes plans for a regional headquarters and in country cloud deployment aligned with Saudi Vision 2030.
